{"tid":1186904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[即call即到]林鄭月娥與駐港領事及商會會面解釋修訂《逃犯條例》","createTime":"2019-06-05T09:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T09:03:14.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe5b381078dff03266a7f08f534d939053aaadf","tid":1186904,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥下午在政府總部分別與外國駐港領事及商會會面，再就修訂《逃犯條例》作交流。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷說，有商會代表向他投訴，昨日下午才收到相關邀請，並被要求即日回覆，感到不被尊重。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，林鄭月娥急於約見商會，反映外國商會、領事能給予特區政府一定壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461109-20190605.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461109-20190605.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=8763c1ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461109-20190605.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3dc4090f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461109-20190605.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}